{
  "texts": [
    "But he would win if he tried to.",
    "Of note is that the notion of 'capability' I use is quite strong.",
    "On a weaker notion, we might say that subject S is capable of achieving X if and only if, when S tries to achieve X, there is a nonnegligible probability that S achieves X.",
    "However, in this paper, I want to explore the case for a strong conclusion: that AI will disempower humanity, not only that there is a nonnegligible probability of human disempowerment through AI.",
    "Thus, I operate with a strong understanding of capability."
  ]
}